1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:02,322
Welcome to Meeting Your Inner Child.

2
00:00:02,322 --> 00:00:06,920
This practice is an invitation to gently
connect with a younger part of you.

3
00:00:06,920 --> 00:00:09,614
You are always allowed to go slowly.

4
00:00:09,614 --> 00:00:11,936
You are allowed to stop.

5
00:00:11,936 --> 00:00:15,791
You are allowed to keep your eyes open.

6
00:00:15,791 --> 00:00:21,271
You do not need to force any memory,
image, or feeling.

7
00:00:21,271 --> 00:00:25,636
Begin by settling into a comfortable
position.

8
00:00:25,636 --> 00:00:30,280
Let your body know that, in this moment,
you are here.

9
00:00:30,280 --> 00:00:33,066
Take a slow breath in.

10
00:00:42,066 --> 00:00:42,066
<break time="3s" />

11
00:00:42,066 --> 00:00:43,599
And release it.

12
00:00:43,599 --> 00:00:45,967
Now notice the room around you.

13
00:00:54,967 --> 00:00:54,967
<break time="3s" />

14
00:00:54,967 --> 00:00:57,614
Notice one thing you can see.

15
00:00:57,614 --> 00:00:59,843
One thing you can feel.

16
00:00:59,843 --> 00:01:02,258
One thing you can hear.

17
00:01:02,258 --> 00:01:05,741
Let this help orient you to the present
moment.

18
00:01:14,741 --> 00:01:14,741
<break time="3s" />

19
00:01:14,741 --> 00:01:19,478
Now imagine, if it feels okay, that there
is a safe inner place.

20
00:01:31,478 --> 00:01:31,478
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

21
00:01:31,478 --> 00:01:37,888
This place can be real or imagined. It
might have warm light, soft colors, a

22
00:01:37,888 --> 00:01:41,648
steady sound, or a sense of quiet
protection.

23
00:01:53,648 --> 00:01:53,648
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

24
00:01:53,648 --> 00:01:55,413
It might be a room.

25
00:01:55,413 --> 00:01:56,249
A garden.

26
00:01:56,249 --> 00:01:56,899
A beach.

27
00:01:56,899 --> 00:01:57,735
A forest.

28
00:01:57,735 --> 00:01:59,082
A cozy chair.

29
00:01:59,082 --> 00:02:01,636
A place with warm light.

30
00:02:01,636 --> 00:02:03,726
Let it be simple.

31
00:02:03,726 --> 00:02:06,884
You are not forcing anything.

32
00:02:06,884 --> 00:02:11,990
You are creating a place where a younger
part could feel safe enough to be

33
00:02:11,990 --> 00:02:12,550
noticed.

34
00:02:12,550 --> 00:02:15,011
Now ask inside:

35
00:02:27,011 --> 00:02:27,011
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

36
00:02:27,011 --> 00:02:31,191
Is there a younger part of me that would
like to be known today?

37
00:02:43,191 --> 00:02:43,191
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

38
00:02:43,191 --> 00:02:45,652
If nothing comes, that is okay.

39
00:02:45,652 --> 00:02:51,435
You can simply sit in this safe place and
offer kindness to any younger parts who

40
00:02:51,435 --> 00:02:52,664
may not be ready.

41
00:02:52,664 --> 00:02:58,794
If a younger part does appear, notice how
close or far away they are.

42
00:03:16,794 --> 00:03:16,794
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

43
00:03:16,794 --> 00:03:20,277
Notice their age, if you sense one.

44
00:03:20,277 --> 00:03:22,878
Notice their expression.

45
00:03:22,878 --> 00:03:25,664
Notice their posture.

46
00:03:25,664 --> 00:03:28,775
Notice what they might be feeling.

47
00:03:28,775 --> 00:03:32,537
You do not need to move toward them too
quickly.

48
00:03:32,537 --> 00:03:34,395
Ask inside:

49
00:03:46,395 --> 00:03:46,395
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

50
00:03:46,395 --> 00:03:49,042
Is it okay if I notice you?

51
00:04:01,042 --> 00:04:01,042
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

52
00:04:01,042 --> 00:04:04,525
If the answer feels like no, respect
that.

53
00:04:04,525 --> 00:04:06,754
You can stay at a distance.

54
00:04:06,754 --> 00:04:13,070
If the answer feels like yes, imagine
offering a gentle presence.

55
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:25,070
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

56
00:04:25,070 --> 00:04:27,485
Now ask this younger part:

57
00:04:39,485 --> 00:04:39,485
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

58
00:04:39,485 --> 00:04:41,435
What do you want me to know?

59
00:04:53,435 --> 00:04:53,435
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

60
00:04:53,435 --> 00:04:54,410
Listen.

61
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:12,410
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

62
00:05:12,410 --> 00:05:13,943
You may hear words.

63
00:05:13,943 --> 00:05:15,754
You may sense feelings.

64
00:05:15,754 --> 00:05:18,401
You may notice images.

65
00:05:18,401 --> 00:05:21,838
You may simply feel something in your
body.

66
00:05:21,838 --> 00:05:23,742
Let it be enough.

67
00:05:41,742 --> 00:05:41,742
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

68
00:05:41,742 --> 00:05:43,228
Now ask:

69
00:05:55,228 --> 00:05:55,228
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

70
00:05:55,228 --> 00:05:56,946
What was hard for you?

71
00:06:08,946 --> 00:06:08,946
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

72
00:06:08,946 --> 00:06:10,246
And then:

73
00:06:10,246 --> 00:06:13,915
What did you need that you did not
receive?

74
00:06:25,915 --> 00:06:25,915
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

75
00:06:25,915 --> 00:06:29,862
If this feels tender, let yourself slow
down.

76
00:06:29,862 --> 00:06:32,463
You do not have to fix it all.

77
00:06:32,463 --> 00:06:34,413
You are simply witnessing.

78
00:06:34,413 --> 00:06:38,082
Now notice how you feel toward this
younger part.

79
00:06:56,082 --> 00:06:56,082
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

80
00:06:56,082 --> 00:07:01,794
If you feel compassion, warmth, or
sadness, let that be here.

81
00:07:01,794 --> 00:07:09,132
If you feel numb, distant, annoyed, or
unsure, notice that too.

82
00:07:09,132 --> 00:07:11,593
That may be another protective part.

83
00:07:11,593 --> 00:07:14,612
You can acknowledge it gently.

84
00:07:14,612 --> 00:07:18,420
If it feels right, say to the younger
part:

85
00:07:18,420 --> 00:07:19,953
I see you.

86
00:07:19,953 --> 00:07:22,600
I believe that this was hard.

87
00:07:22,600 --> 00:07:24,829
You deserved care.

88
00:07:24,829 --> 00:07:27,708
I am here with you now.

89
00:07:27,708 --> 00:07:30,866
Notice how the younger part responds.

90
00:07:48,866 --> 00:07:48,866
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s"
/><break time="3s" />

91
00:07:48,866 --> 00:07:50,027
You might ask:

92
00:07:50,027 --> 00:07:53,603
What would help you feel a little safer
right now?

93
00:08:05,603 --> 00:08:05,603
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

94
00:08:05,603 --> 00:08:07,136
Maybe they want space.

95
00:08:07,136 --> 00:08:08,529
Maybe closeness.

96
00:08:08,529 --> 00:08:10,433
Maybe a blanket.

97
00:08:10,433 --> 00:08:12,058
Maybe a kind word.

98
00:08:12,058 --> 00:08:14,612
Maybe a place to play.

99
00:08:14,612 --> 00:08:17,956
Maybe simply not to be rushed.

100
00:08:17,956 --> 00:08:21,811
Imagine offering only what feels welcome.

101
00:08:33,811 --> 00:08:33,811
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

102
00:08:33,811 --> 00:08:38,734
Now thank this younger part for showing
up in whatever way they did.

103
00:08:38,734 --> 00:08:42,496
Let them know you can return slowly.

104
00:08:51,496 --> 00:08:51,496
<break time="3s" />

105
00:08:51,496 --> 00:08:54,050
You do not have to leave them behind.

106
00:08:54,050 --> 00:08:59,437
You can imagine placing them somewhere
safe and comfortable inside.

107
00:09:11,437 --> 00:09:11,437
<break time="3s" /><break time="3s" />

108
00:09:11,437 --> 00:09:14,734
Now begin to notice your adult body
again.

109
00:09:14,734 --> 00:09:15,709
Your breath.

110
00:09:15,709 --> 00:09:17,474
The surface under you.

111
00:09:17,474 --> 00:09:20,168
The room around you.

112
00:09:20,168 --> 00:09:23,279
Take one slow breath in.

113
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:32,279
<break time="3s" />

114
00:09:32,279 --> 00:09:34,508
And let it out.

115
00:09:34,508 --> 00:09:38,363
When you are ready, gently return.

116
00:09:38,363 --> 00:09:44,292
You do not have to complete the whole
story today. Simply noticing a younger

117
00:09:44,292 --> 00:09:50,457
part with care is already a meaningful
act of repair. You can come back slowly,

118
00:09:50,457 --> 00:09:53,224
with patience, warmth, and respect.

119
00:09:53,224 --> 00:09:56,196
------------------------------------------
------------------------------.

